Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 Cosplay Vtuber 普洛佩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这次COS的是地狱鲨鱼伯格5中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,琪拉薇尔唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的直播 我打算在清晨的新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,试着教乌鸦说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 还是一样胡闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都凌晨三点了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 总觉得这条街变得有点冷喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 怎么看就在这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是乌鸦先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喵 你们在看哪里喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,手 是手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喵！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噗
